==English==
===Alternative spellings===
In some usages (particularly old documents), words in the phrase may be capitalized, for example '''[[Party of the Second Part]]'''.
===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[party]] [[of]] [[the]] [[second]] [[part]]|pl=parties of the second part}}
#{{law}}{{archaic}}: the [[party]] to a [[legal]] [[dispute]] against whom a [[complaint]] was initially raised in a [[court]]
#{{law}}{{archaic}}: the second party named in a [[contract]], generally the party to whom a duty is initially owed, and who is obligated to perform in response to the performance of that initial duty

